OL,3,CMan charged with murders of wife and
OL,4,Cdaughters of racing commentator John
OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FKyle Clifford has appeared in court
OL,8,Fthis morning, charged with the murders
OL,9,Fof Hannah, Louise and Carol Hunt, in
OL,10,FBushey, Hertfordshire, as Chloe Keedy
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FA 26-year-old man accused of killing
OL,14,Fthe wife and two daughters of a BBC
OL,15,Fracing commentator John Hunt in a
OL,16,Fcrossbow attack has appeared in court
OL,17,Ftoday.
