OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FKyle Clifford was remanded in custody
OL,8,Fat Westminster Magistrates' Court and
OL,9,Fthen at the Royal Courts of Justice on
OL,10,FTuesday afternoon following the
OL,11,Fincident in Bushey, Hertfordshire, on
OL,12,FJuly 9.
OL,14,FLouise Hunt, 25, and her sister
OL,15,FHannah, 28, had been shot with a
OL,16,Fcrossbow and their mother Carol Hunt ,
OL,17,F61, had been stabbed with a knife and
OL,18,Fsuffered multiple injuries, the court
OL,19,Fwas told.
