OL,7,FClifford has been remanded into
OL,8,Fcustody, and will appear at the Royal
OL,9,FCourts of Justice this afternoon.
OL,11,FHe has been under arrest since July
OL,12,F10, but police were unable to speak to
OL,13,Fhim while he received treatment for an
OL,14,Finjury in hospital.
