OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FThe 26-year-old also faces two counts
OL,8,Fof possession of an offensive weapon `
OL,9,Fone a 10-inch butcher's knife and the
OL,10,Fother a compound crossbow.
OL,12,FThe defendant faces a final count of
OL,13,Ffalse imprisonment which alleges that
OL,14,Fhe "assaulted and unlawfully and
OL,15,Finjuriously imprisoned Louise Hunt and
OL,16,Fdetained her against her will".
