OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Nick
OL,8,FGardner, from the Bedfordshire,
OL,9,FCambridgeshire and Hertfordshire Major
OL,10,FCrime Unit, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,11,Fwith the Hunt family and their loved
OL,12,Fones as they continue to come to terms
OL,13,Fwith their loss.
OL,15,F"Over the past couple of months, we
OL,16,Fhave been working hard to gather as
OL,17,Fmuch evidence as possible and
OL,18,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,19,Fwhat happened that day.
