OL,5,CHunt
OL,7,F"Today, we have managed to secure
OL,8,Fcharges against Kyle Clifford in
OL,9,Fconnection with the murders of Carol,
OL,10,FHannah and Louise Hunt.
OL,12,F"Although it has taken some time to
OL,13,Freach this stage, we can now move
OL,14,Fforward with the judicial process and
OL,15,Fseek justice for their family."
